psalm.text:
[[Ps 132,6]]"Behold, we have heard of it in Ephrathah; 
we have found it in the fields of Jaar.
[[Ps 132,7]]Let us enter God's dwelling; 
let us worship at God's footstool."

[[Ps 132,8]]"Arise, LORD, come to your resting place, 
you and your majestic ark.
[[Ps 132,9]]Your priests will be clothed with justice; 
your faithful will shout for joy."
[[Ps 132,10]]For the sake of David your servant, 
do not reject your anointed.
